
// This Hyperlambda code checks if the value of [items-left] is less than 10. If true, it sets the value of [restock-alert] to "Inventory low!". The [if] slot evaluates the condition, and the [.lambda] block executes the action if the condition is met.
if
   lt:x:@.items-left
      .:int:10
   .lambda
      set-value:x:@.restock-alert
         .:Inventory low!
